          <title>Sinner crushes Zverev to win Madrid Open and claim record 5th straight Masters 1000 title</title>
          <description><![CDATA[Top-ranked Jannik Sinner has cruised past Alexander Zverev in the final of the Madrid Open to win the tournament for the first time and become the first man to triumph in five consecutive Masters 1000 events.]]></description>
